> And for buyers who genuinely prefer round but are deterred by the price: the lab market at $1,560 for D-IF Ideal removes the price barrier completely. There is no longer a financial reason to compromise on the shape you actually want." — Farzana Hasan, **[Diamond Critics](https://diamondcritics.com/about-farzana/)**

